name: Girl Fashion Runner
summary: Dive into the glamorous world of "Girl Fashion Runner," a thrilling VR experience where style meets speed! Navigate through bustling cityscapes and stunning landscapes, collecting fashion items and avoiding obstacles. Customize your avatar with chic outfits and accessories to enhance your run. Perfect for fashionistas seeking adventure, this game combines immersive environments with heart-pounding action. Join the runway, where every race is a fashion statement!
